### What _is_ Plexicraft?
Plexicraft is a collection of everything!
It has: Plexicraft-core, Plexichat, Flexums, Plexigames, Pleximedia

### How to start a custom server
Plexicraft allows you to create a custom server, or _alternate universe_ as they call it.
Just clone or download the project, then run `npm start`.

### How to connect to your custom server
To connect to your custom server, go to [the plexicraft site](bit.ly/plexicraft) and enter the following
commands into the f12 developer console:

ws = new WebSocket("ws://localhost:5000");

